<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Support Request Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4A90E2;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .message-box {
      background-color: #fff;
      border-left: 4px solid #4A90E2;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .info {
      background-color: #e7f3fe;
      border-left: 4px solid #2196F3;
      padding: 10px;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Support Request Received</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
      <p>Thank you for submitting a support request to 3DVN. We have received your request and will process it as soon as possible.</p>
      
      <div class="info">
        <p><strong>Request ID:</strong> {{requestId}}</p>
      </div>

      <h3>Your request content:</h3>
      <div class="message-box">
        <p>{{message}}</p>
      </div>

      <p>Our support team will review your request and respond as soon as possible. The typical response time is 24-48 business hours.</p>
      
      <p>If you have additional information or questions, please reply to this email or reference the request ID above.</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>The 3DVN Support Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Â© {{year}} 3DVN. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This email was sent to {{email}}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>